snippet.title: OWN trailer
snippet.description:
Come and play On the Way to Nemroth (OWN)! OWN is a new online game with no download nor install, and is 100% free-to-play!

Pick a hero and fight your opponents in 1v1, 2v2 and 3v3 in super-fast matches!

Register and unlock a free legendary chest : https://www.nemroth.com !

Follow us on social medias : 
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/OWN-en-1748466661849358/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/OWNemroth_en?lang=fr
Twitch : https://www.twitch.tv/OWN_fr
Discord : https://discord.gg/3eakaFD
